The traffic in Mexico City is now in a particularly poor state.
This city is overloaded with transport and at a better time, and since Monday steel barriers have been built, cutting several key roads to the capital and causing chaos on the roads.
However, this was not done to prevent people from getting to work from the suburbs, but to prevent protesters from reaching the parliamentary building.
